### Create Razorpay Order
POST {{baseUrl}}/institutes/payment/create-order
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Verify Razorpay Payment (or Legacy /payment)
POST {{baseUrl}}/institutes/payment/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "razorpay_order_id": "REPLACE_WITH_ORDER_ID_FROM_CREATE_ORDER_RESPONSE",
  "razorpay_payment_id": "pay_mock_123456",
  "razorpay_signature": "mock_signature_hex_code_if_real_mode"
}




### Review Application (Board/Admin)
# Replace INSTITUTE_ID_HERE with a valid ObjectId
POST {{baseUrl}}/institutes/INSTITUTE_ID_HERE/review
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Approved",
  "remarks": "All documentation, infrastructure, and faculty checks have successfully passed."
}

### ==========================================
### 6. MODULE 3 — ELIGIBILITY ENGINE (Use Case 3.1)
### ==========================================

### 6.1 List All Courses (GET /api/academic/courses)
GET {{baseUrl}}/academic/courses
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6.2 List All Batches (GET /api/academic/batches)
GET {{baseUrl}}/academic/batches
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6.3 List All Students with Eligibility Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/academic/students
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6.4 List Eligible Students Only
GET {{baseUrl}}/academic/students?isEligible=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6.5 List Not-Eligible Students Only
GET {{baseUrl}}/academic/students?isEligible=false
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6.6 Search Students by Name or Enrollment ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/academic/students?search=SEMI
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6.7 Update Academic Metrics for a Student (PATCH)
# Replace STUDENT_ID_HERE with a real student _id from the list above
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/academic/students/STUDENT_ID_HERE/academic-metrics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "attendancePercentage": 82,
  "thesisApproved": true
}

### 6.8 Evaluate Eligibility for a Specific Student (GET)
# Replace STUDENT_ID_HERE with a real student _id
GET {{baseUrl}}/academic/students/STUDENT_ID_HERE/eligibility
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6.9 Make Student NOT Eligible (low attendance, thesis pending)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/academic/students/STUDENT_ID_HERE/academic-metrics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "attendancePercentage": 60,
  "thesisApproved": false
}
